T02D3530:171b-1: sv'a dh'ishth'a na kra ma m'a r'i tsyee s'a dha nam /
T02D3530:171b-3: rang byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa'i 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3530:171b-4: 'phags ma 'od zer can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3530:171b-5: dang por re zhig rang gi snying gar nyi ma'i
T02D3530:171b-6: gdan la h'um yig gi 'od zer gyis bcom ldan
T02D3530:171b-8: dpag tu med pa'i mchod pa rnams kyis yang dag
T02D3530:171b-9: par mchod nas sdig pa bshags pa la sogs pa
T02D3530:171b-10: byas te / stong ba nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes la
T02D3530:171b-11: sna tshogs rdo rje'i rnam pa sems kyis bsams te
T02D3530:171b-12: byas te / / de yongs su gyur pa las
T02D3530:171b-13: rdo rje'i sa gzhi dang rdo rje'i ra ba la

T02D3530:172a-3: phyag g-yon pa rnams su sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i khab dang /

T02D3530:172a-9: mi mgo'i phreng ba 'phyang bas yan lag dang nying lag thams cad brgyan pa /
T02D3530:172a-10: stag gi pags pa'i stod g-yogs can /
T02D3530:172a-13: nag po ni g-yon pa'i zhal gnyis so //
T02D3530:172a-15: nag po ni g-yas pa'i zhal gnyis so //
T02D3530:172a-16: steng du ni phag zhal nag po'o //
T02D3530:172a-17: ljags 'dril zhing skra kham pa gyen du 'bar ba /

T02D3530:172a-21: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i mkha' 'gro ma dang /
T02D3530:172a-25: ha ha zhes 'jigs pa'i sgra sgrogs pas yongs su bskor ba'i dur khrod brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
T02D3530:172a-26: dpal ldan ao di y'a na'i 'od zer can gyi
T02D3530:172a-27: bdag nyid du skad cig gis bskyed la mgo bo
